        Returns all the seat maps of a given flightOffer. This operation allows to retrieve the seat map of each flight included in a flight offer. Consumer can request the seat map for up to 6 flight Offer in the same query. The reply is a list of seat map linked to its impacted segment and flight offer. The endpoint is owned by defaultname service owner
